description: In honor of Michael Jackson's memory, the National Visionary Leadership Project offers this clip where Quincy Jones speaks about meeting Michael Jackson on the set of The Wiz and subsequently working with him on Off The Wall. To see more oral history interview clips with Quincy Jones, visit: http://www.visionaryproject.org/jonesquincy
title: Quincy Jones talks about Michael Jackson
